data.description: Welcome to this charming residence in the desirable Charleston Park neighborhood, nestled at 3917 N Hanover Place, Tyler, Texas. This immaculate 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a generous living space of 2,691 square feet, providing ample room for comfortable living and entertaining. Built in 2001, this timeless abode seamlessly combines modern convenience with classic design elements. Step inside to discover a well-appointed interior that exudes both warmth and elegance. The spacious open floor plan effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings and daily life. Natural light filters through large windows, accentuating the beauty of the living spaces. The gourmet kitchen boasts a perfect blend of style and functionality. Featuring modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a convenient layout, it's a haven for culinary enthusiasts. The adjacent dining area is ideal for both casual family meals and formal dinners, making every occasion special. Unwind in the inviting primary bedroom suite, complete with an en-suite bathroom that includes dual sinks, a luxurious soaking tub, and a separate shower. Three additional well-proportioned bedrooms offer comfort and privacy for family members or guests. The home's 2.5 bathrooms feature elegant fixtures and finishes that add a touch of luxury. A highlight of this property is its outdoor space. The landscaped yard provides a tranquil setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or relaxation. The covered patio is perfect for enjoying the mild Texas climate, whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional house your new home.
